    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It is possible to create a key that is able to only get the settings. But that requires to have a new custom key generated by the user... Would also require to have the plumbing to create the first query to check the configuration.\r\n\r\nMaybe that could be a dev tool? Offline check before the production?",
