    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "When a parameter is not recognized, it returns an error and this pretty fast to see with the initial search. For the parameters that are not throwing an error, we only have the facets as a use but we didn't have much problems so far with that. Let's close this issue for now and revisit if we get a brilliant idea or if we identify a pain.",
